thread.title: Deiadora Blanche

author: Deiadora Blanche
title: Deiadora Blanche
text: Wow, wow, wow! I could not have received better service at LaserAway in La Jolla. I would highly recommend this facility to anyone looking for laser tattoo removal. The staff was highly organised, personable, and professional. They took great care to ensure that I was comfortable and the procedure was completed by a nurse practitioner. I will be returning until my tattoo is gone!
